flowchart LR
    A[Raw Text Input] --> B[Text Cleaning<br/>Lowercasing, Normalization]
    B --> C[Pre-Tokenization<br/>Whitespace & Punctuation Split]
    C --> D[Subword Tokenization<br/>BPE / WordPiece / SentencePiece]
    D --> E[Token to ID Mapping<br/>Vocabulary Lookup]
    E --> F[Model Input<br/>Embeddings + Attention]
    F --> G[Model Output IDs]
    G --> H[Decoder<br/>IDs → Tokens → Text]
